OL,3,CRandom presenting rotas damaging BBC
OL,4,CNews brand?
OL,6,GDoes it matter who reads the news? It
OL,7,Gmay seem like a stupid question. News
OL,8,Gpresenters are not personalities. As
OL,9,Glong as the presenter is acceptable
OL,10,Gand doing their job professionally,
OL,11,Gshould it matter?
OL,13,FThe truth is it does.
OL,15,FRegular presenters build up a
OL,16,Frelationship with viewers ` if nothing
OL,17,Felse, regular presenters become a
OL,18,Ffamiliar part of the everyday lives of
OL,19,Fviewers.
