OL,3,CRandom presenting rotas damaging BBC
OL,4,CNews brand?
OL,6,FEven if presenters are not marketed or
OL,7,Fpromoted as such, they are part of the
OL,8,Fprogramme's brand.
OL,10,FSo, having said why presenters matter
OL,11,Fis it time for the BBC to look again
OL,12,Fat the rota for the main BBC One news
OL,13,Fprogrammes.
OL,15,FThe rota seems to have become rather
OL,16,Frandom.
OL,18,FThe absence of Huw Edwards, the death
OL,19,Fof George Alagiah and the impact of
OL,20,Fthe major changes to the BBC News
OL,21,FChannel all seem to have played a part.
