OL,3,CRandom presenting rotas damaging BBC
OL,4,CNews brand?
OL,6,FThere are nights when the Six and Ten
OL,7,Fshare a presenter ` and nights when
OL,8,Fthey do not.
OL,10,FThere is no sense of a relationship
OL,11,Fbetween particular news programmes and
OL,12,Fpresenters ` some seem as likely to do
OL,13,Fone programme as another.
OL,15,FAnd some unfamiliar faces are
OL,16,Fpresenting the weekend lunchtime
OL,17,Fbulletins.
OL,19,FIt is time for consistency to return `
OL,20,Fa smaller team of familiar,
OL,21,Frecognisable faces.
