OL,3,CRandom presenting rotas damaging BBC
OL,4,CNews brand?
OL,6,FWhen the BBC overhauled news
OL,7,Fprogrammes in 1999, the rota was
OL,8,Fsimple.
OL,10,
OL,11,F Anna Ford usually presented the One
OL,12,Fwith Darren Jordan usually covering on
OL,13,Fother days.
OL,14,F Huw Edwards was the face of the Six
OL,15,Fwith Fiona Bruce in the chair on
OL,16,FFridays.
OL,17,F Peter Sissons and Michael Buerk
OL,18,Fcontinued as the presenters of the
OL,19,FNine.
