OL,3,CRandom presenting rotas damaging BBC
OL,4,CNews brand?
OL,6,FThese changes were also a reminder
OL,7,Fthat presenting is a precarious
OL,8,Foccupation. Martyn Lewis left and a
OL,9,Fnumber of others either returned to
OL,10,Freporting or stopped presenting
OL,11,Fregularly.
OL,13,FI'd suggest the following rota.
OL,15,FThe One and the Six should share the
OL,16,Fsame presenter. There should be only
OL,17,Ftwo people allowed to front the
OL,18,Fprogramme regularly.
OL,20,FTwo presenters should be devoted to
OL,21,Fthe Ten, taking it in turns to present
OL,22,Facross the whole week.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/7
