OL,3,CRandom presenting rotas damaging BBC
OL,4,CNews brand?
OL,6,FThe weekend lunchtime and early
OL,7,Fevening bulletins should also have a
OL,8,Fdedicated presenter.
OL,10,FThis would mean a smaller team of
OL,11,Ffamiliar faces and would also allow
OL,12,Fthe Ten to maintain a degree of a
OL,13,Fdistinct personality.
OL,15,FThere would, inevitably, be difficult
OL,16,Fchoices if fewer people were given
OL,17,Fpresenting shifts and some would be
OL,18,Fdisappointed. But such is the nature
OL,19,Fof what should always be a
OL,20,Fprestigious, high-profile role.
