OL,3,CRandom presenting rotas damaging BBC
OL,4,CNews brand?
OL,6,FPresenting the news is not a
OL,7,Fpersonality contest. But viewers like
OL,8,Ffamiliarity.
OL,10,FHaving fewer presenters would mean a
OL,11,Fstronger brand image.
OL,13,FPresenting the news on BBC One network
OL,14,Fshould always be an honour, not a
OL,15,Fmatter of balancing the rota.
